g.title: ArthurRank3Convo6 begins.
g.text: ArthurRank3Convo6 begins.

g.title: j3738979994
g.text: Let's trade hostage facts.

g.title: j911438234
g.text: LOL what?

g.title: j4196501286
g.text: The past is weird.

g.title: j3999457399
g.text: Heh. So. This is a game I used to play in the Britannic Army.

g.title: j4140261527
g.text: You tell me an embarrassing fact about yourself, and I tell you one about myself.

g.title: j2758034086
g.text: We hold each other's facts hostage.

g.title: j2623620373
g.text: Hostage facts. It's a "trust exercise." I'll even go first.

g.title: j1601460538
g.text: Normally, I think you're supposed to go to a ropes course... but fine.

g.title: j3588924527
g.text: Sure. Why not.

g.title: j4148185603
g.text: Nah. I'm out.

g.title: j2911005043
g.text: Here's mine: I own a teddy bear named Sebastian.

g.title: j3032033183
g.text: Suit yourself.

g.title: j3923415050
g.text: Now, before you get it in your head that I snuggle up with him at night, I don't.

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j1648034200
g.text: I found him on a mission, in a bombed out housing block, years ago.

g.title: j3870761154
g.text: I keep him on a shelf. And when I've got nobody else to talk to?

g.title: j1714352491
g.text: I talk to him. Ratty old fella. Keeps me from going nuts.

g.title: j250633461
g.text: ROFLMAO

g.title: j472910058
g.text: That is... painfully adorable.

g.title: j2460202099
g.text: Can I hug Sebastian at some point?

g.title: j2304234920
g.text: Yeah, yeah.

g.title: j4156848780
g.text: I think I just died a little.

g.title: j2543856896
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1218254237
g.text: I might pee I'm laughing so hard! lol

g.title: j3647575743
g.text: You're full of surprises, Arthur.

g.title: j2965904136
g.text: Don't see why not.

g.title: j1840295472
g.text: Yeah, I get it.

g.title: j3589551388
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j4064208578
g.text: Your turn.

g.title: j794074452
g.text: Heh.

g.title: j2487429608
g.text: On Duviri, I kept accidentally summoning my childhood bedroom because I wanted somewhere to hide.

g.title: j1102285261
g.text: One time, when I was decapitated by Lodun, my head flew off so hard it wound up in a tree!

g.title: j3752122082
g.text: It took me six hundred and eighty-seven loops to learn how to properly ride a kaithe.

g.title: j3794178146
g.text: No, I'll pass. But thanks for telling me about Sebastian.

g.title: j272187764
g.text: I've lost track of how many bedrooms I summoned by the time I figured out how to get out of there.

g.title: j856288757
g.text: Do you know how long the head stays alive after it's been cut off? Because *I DO.* LOL

g.title: j2477503793
g.text: I started tallying all my broken bones. I think I still have the list somewhere.

g.title: j662660886
g.text: Should've known.

g.title: j2116415315
g.text: Dear Sol... I think you misunderstood the assignment here, mate.

g.title: j1204444816
g.text: But, uh - thanks for trying.
